{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-generic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/a2-english-for-developers/learn-how-to-ask-and-share-about-educational-and-professional-background/task-86","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"assignments":[],"bilibiliIds":null,"block":"learn-how-to-ask-and-share-about-educational-and-professional-background","challengeType":19,"description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Sve <span class=\"highlighted-text\">therapist</span> i <span class=\"highlighted-text\">counselor</span> pomažu ljude sa njihovim osećanjima i problemima, ali postoji mala razlika:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">counselor</span> obično pruža kratkoročnu podršku. Sasluša ljude, daje savete i pomaže im da reše određene probleme, kao što su stres na poslu ili porodične poteškoće.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">therapist</span> obično pruža dugoročnu podršku. Često ima više stručne obuke i radi sa ozbiljnijim problemima mentalnog zdravlja, kao što su anksioznost, depresija ili emocionalna trauma.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>","nodules":null,"explanation":null,"helpCategory":"English","instructions":"","fields":{"slug":"/learn/a2-english-for-developers/learn-how-to-ask-and-share-about-educational-and-professional-background/task-86"},"questions":[{"text":"<p>Na šta se u Anninoj izjavi odnosi izraz <span class=\"highlighted-text\">therapist or counselor</span>?</p>","answers":[{"answer":"<p>Rad u sektorima tehnologije.</p>","feedback":"<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Therapist or counselor</span> odnosi se na zanimanja iz oblasti mentalnog zdravlja i emocionalne podrške, a ne na poslove povezane sa tehnologijom.</p>","audioId":null},{"answer":"<p>Rad na mentalnom zdravlju i emocionalnoj podršci.</p>","feedback":null,"audioId":null},{"answer":"<p>Želio je da pohađa edukativni kurs.</p>","feedback":"<p>Iako ova zanimanja zahtevaju obrazovanje, ovi izrazi se direktno odnose na profesije, a ne na kurseve.</p>","audioId":null},{"answer":"<p>Michezo au shughuli alizopenda.</p>","feedback":"<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Therapist or counselor</span> su profesionalni karijerni putevi, a ne sportovi ili rekreativne aktivnosti.</p>","audioId":null}],"solution":2}],"scene":{"setup":{"background":"company2-parking.png","characters":[{"character":"Anna","position":{"x":50,"y":15,"z":1.2},"opacity":0}],"audio":{"filename":"3.1-5.mp3","startTime":1,"startTimestamp":6.96,"finishTimestamp":11.36},"alwaysShowDialogue":null},"commands":[{"background":null,"character":"Anna","position":null,"opacity":1,"startTime":0,"finishTime":null,"dialogue":null},{"background":null,"character":"Anna","position":null,"opacity":null,"startTime":1,"finishTime":5.4,"dialogue":{"text":"I actually studied psychology in college. My plan was to become a therapist or counselor.","align":"center"}},{"background":null,"character":"Anna","position":null,"opacity":0,"startTime":5.9,"finishTime":null,"dialogue":null}]},"superBlock":"a2-english-for-developers","tests":[],"title":"Vežba 86","transcript":null,"translationPending":false,"videoId":null,"videoLocaleIds":null}}},"pageContext":{"challengeMeta":{"blockHashSlug":"/learn/a2-english-for-developers/#learn-how-to-ask-and-share-about-educational-and-professional-background","dashedName":"task-86","certification":"a2-english-for-developers","disableLoopProtectTests":false,"disableLoopProtectPreview":false,"superBlock":"a2-english-for-developers","chapter":null,"module":null,"block":"learn-how-to-ask-and-share-about-educational-and-professional-background","isFirstStep":false,"template":null,"required":[],"isLastChallengeInBlock":false,"nextChallengePath":"/learn/a2-english-for-developers/learn-how-to-ask-and-share-about-educational-and-professional-background/task-87","prevChallengePath":"/learn/a2-english-for-developers/learn-how-to-ask-and-share-about-educational-and-professional-background/task-85","id":"657b2f0b3bcfe7d9f4151854","saveSubmiss